able until June 30.  Despite collecting Rs 11 crore, collections are down from last year.  PMC is urging taxpayers to pay, with defaulters facing 1.5% monthly interest from October.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/patna-municipal-corporation-offers-40-lakh-rebate-for-early-property-tax-payments/130977287?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-233398/130977287.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}